snippet.title: Preimplantation genetic testing (PGT)  - for whom and how does it help?
snippet.description:
Dr. Luca Gianaroli, Scientific Director of S.I.S.Me.R., is talking about PGT (preimplantation genetic testing), results and indications for such a test.
